Package: DHaushaltR
Title: German Federal Digital Budget Data (2019-2025)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Juan", "Vivanco", email = "jvivanco@ikmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Provides the cleaned dataset from the Agora Digitale Transformation
    research project on Germany's federal digital budget ('Digitalhaushalt').
    The dataset covers budget lines tagged for digitalisation across five fiscal
    years (2019, 2021, 2023, 2024, 2025), including thematic digital categories,
    detection method flags, and resolved Funktionenplan codes. Companion lookup
    tables map all code columns to human-readable German labels.
